  "decision_conditions": [
    "&lt;p&gt;The proposed development, by reason of its height, depth and&amp;nbsp; scale would comprise an overly dominant development, to the detriment of the living conditions of residential occupiers of No.51 Ufton Road by way of a loss of light, outlook, overlooking and increased sense of enclosure to the window at upper ground floor, contrary to Hackney Local Plan (LP33) policy LP2 (Design and Amenity) and Hackneys &#x27;Residential Extensions and Alterations&#x27; SPD (2009).&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;",
    "&lt;p&gt;The proposed development, by reason of its siting, scale and detailed design, would result in an obtrusive, overbearing and incompatible form of development which would fail to respect the character and appearance of the subject property and the conservation area of which it forms part.&amp;nbsp; As such the proposed development is contrary to policy D4 &#x27;Delivering good design&#x27; of the London Plan (2021) and Policies LP1 (Design Quality and Local Character), LP3 (Designated heritage assets) of the Hackney Local Plan and the guidance contained within Hackney Residential Extensions and Alterations SPD 2009.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;"
  ],
